        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "在Ni10%@β/M催化剂上，于160°C、5 MPa初始氢压下，对从煤焦油残渣中提取的富含酚类的可溶部分(PEEPM)进行16小时的催化加氢转化(CHC)，得到CHPEEPM。产物中环烷烃相对含量高达93.4%。",
        "text_snippet": "Approximately 100mg PEEPM, 100mg Ni10%@β/M, and 20mL n-hexane were placed in a 100mL miniature autoclave, sealed, and purged of air. The hydrofinishing reaction was carried out for 16h at 5MPa IHP and 160◦C.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "加氢反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "使用模型化合物苯甲氧基苯(BOB)在Ni10%@β/M催化剂上研究催化活性。反应在160°C、5 MPa初始氢压下进行2小时，BOB完全转化为环烷烃。",
        "text_snippet": "In a standard CHC process, 100 mg BOB, 50 mg Ni10%@β/M, and 20 mL n-hexane were carefully mixed and introduced into a miniaturized autoclave... heated to a temperature range of 160 ◦C for durations of 120 min.",
